-- Canada Dollar Erases Drop as Bernanke Backs Continued Stimulus
-- B y   K e n n e t h   P r i n g l e
-- 2013-05-22T14:07:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-22/canada-dollar-erases-drop-as-bernanke-backs-continued-stimulus.html
The Canadian dollar erased a decline
against its U.S. peer after Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said premature tightening of central-bank policy would
endanger the U.S. economic recovery.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
